---
title: Baked Potatoes and Smoky Portobello Bites with Cheddar Broccoli and Green Onions
description: We're serving up a pub classic, but minus the meat! Thin slices of savoury portobello mushrooms are rubbed in spices and baked until crisp for a veggie take on bacon bits!
